<DATELINE>
   BONN
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Hugo Boss, Germany's best known menswear manufacturer, yesterday raised its
annual dividend after reporting record profits of DM76.5m (Dollars 45.6m).
Ordinary shares will receive a DM23 dividend, up from DM21, while holders of
preferential stock will receive DM24.50, also up DM2.
